<ab facs="#facs_216_r1l17">niht anheim ıſt . vvenn er <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> heim kombt <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> wır denn daran </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_216_r1l18">gemant ſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır Jn <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ʒu rede <expan>ſecʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> . vnd <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
