<ab facs="#facs_216_r1l20">von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> Otten <expan>ledr<ex>er</ex>s</expan> des heffners <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> . wıe der der </ab>
