<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr gnade
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von Conczen Gawchs, des
                                <expan>heffn<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>, <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                        gnade <add>wissen</add>, daz <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>C<ex>oncz</ex></expan> Gawch zu <expan>dis<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> niht anheim ist. Wenn er
                            <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> heim kombt, <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>
                        wir denn daran gemant, so <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir in
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> zu rede <expan>secze<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> sein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> zu
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> tun. Als uns denn ewr gnade
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> Otten <expan>Ledr<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, des
                        heffners, <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, wie der der heffner hantwerk über
                        land <expan>gebrawch<ex>en</ex></expan> well etc., den
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir für uns besant und
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu rede gesaczt. Der hat uns
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, daz er in der heffner eynung niht
                        sey und auch darein niht main zu <expan>kom<ex>m</ex>en</expan>. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Egidii. </ab>
</div>
